imdb.plot outline: Think Tony Robbins meets Access Hollywood: personal development, excellence training and success strategies. Hollywood CEO is shot live on location at some of the hottest entertainment industry events. Learn from award winning producers, directors, writers, actors, music artists and CEO's. Discover specific strategies on how they have successfully managed some of their biggest challenges. Apply these techniques and principle's to your life and create your own success.
